//sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/ramayanagorr/?3,68,44 target=_blank rel=noopener>3,68,44</a>. <i class=sa>mā gantumarhasi</i> <span class=ab>st.</span> <i class=sa>na ga˚</i> metrically <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/ramayanagorr/?2,116,5 target=_blank rel=noopener>2,116,5</a>.", "dcs": 4955, "src": "attested"}, {"tag": "§v5", "de_html": "<b>3.</b> √<i class=sa>mā</i>¦ V. 5.", "ru_html": "V. 5.", "en_html": "<b>3.</b> √<i class=sa>mā</i> — V. 5.", "dcs": 4955, "src": "attested"}, {"tag": "§v5ati", "de_html": "— Mit <i class=sa>ā</i> 5.", "ru_html": "— Mit <i class=sa>ā</i> 5.", "en_html": "— With <i class=sa>ā</i> 5.", "dcs": 4955, "src": "attested"}, {"tag": "§v5pra", "de_html": "— Mit <i class=sa>pra</i> <span class=ab>Desid.</span> sich über Etwas (<span class=ab>Acc.</span>) eine richtige Vorstellung zu bilden wünschen <span class=ls>BHĀMATĪ 616,9</span>.", "ru_html": "— Mit <i class=sa>pra</i> <span class=ab>Desid.</span> желать составить правильное представление о чём-либо (<span class=ab>Acc.</span>) <span class=ls>BHĀMATĪ 616,9</span>.", "en_html": "— With <i class=sa>pra</i> <span class=ab>Desid.</span> &quot;to wish to form a correct idea about something&quot; (<span class=ab>Acc.</span>) <span class=ls>BHĀMATĪ 616,9</span>.", "dcs": 4955, "src": "attested"}, {"tag": "§v5sam", "de_html": "— Mit <i class=sa>sam</i> V. 5.", "ru_html": "— Mit <i class=sa>sam</i> V. 5.", "en_html": "— With <i class=sa>sam</i> V. 5.", "dcs": 4955, "src": "attested"}, {"tag": "1", "de_html": "<b>4.</b> <i class=sa>mā</i>¦ <span class=lex>f.</span><br>— 1〉 Maass.", "ru_html": "1〉 мера.", "en_html": "", "dcs": 4955, "src": "attested"}, {"tag": "mit T29 — 1", "de_html": "— Mit <i class=sa>apa</i><br>— 1〉 durch Tausch vergüten, heimgeben. Nur <i class=sa>apabhitya</i>.", "ru_html": "— Mit <i class=sa>apa</i><br>1〉 воздавать посредством обмена, возвращать. Только <i class=sa>apabhitya</i>.", "en_html": "", "dcs": 4955, "src": "attested"}, {"tag": "mit T60 — 1", "de_html": "— Mit <i class=sa>ā</i> 1〉 bilden, hervorbringen <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv03.038.html#rv03.038.07 target=_blank rel=noopener>ṚV. 3,38,7</a>.", "ru_html": "— Mit <i class=sa>ā</i> 1〉 создавать, производить <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv03.038.html#rv03.038.07 target=_blank rel=noopener>ṚV. 3,38,7</a>.", "en_html": "", "dcs": 4955, "src": "attested"}, {"tag": "mit T60 — 2", "de_html": "— 2〉 herbeischaffen <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv10.056.html#rv10.056.02 target=_blank rel=noopener>ṚV. 10,56,2</a>.", "ru_html": "2〉 добывать, доставлять <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv10.056.html#rv10.056.02 target=_blank rel=noopener>ṚV. 10,56,2</a>.", "en_html": "", "dcs": 4955, "src": "attested"}]}, {"key": "m_a~~h0_zz_sch", "h": "1. mā (частица) — SCH", "iast": "mā", "senses": [{"tag": "1", "de_html": "mā¦ mit Praes. damit nicht, <span class=ls>R. Gorr. 1,65,21.</span> purā mā mit Praes. so v.a. sonst, andernfalls,3,68,44. mā gantum arhasi metrisch statt na gan˚,2,116,5.", "ru_html": "", "en_html": "mā¦ with Praes. so that not, <span class=ls>R. Gorr. 1,65,21.</span> purā mā with Praes. so v.a. otherwise, else, 3,68,44. mā gantum arhasi metrically for na gan˚, 2,116,5.", "dcs": null, "src": ""}, {"tag": "3", "de_html": "mā¦ 15. mitá neben sáṃmita <span class=ls>Maitr. S. 2,11,1</span> (140,4). — Mit ā 1. bilden, hervorbringen, <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv03.038.html#rv03.038.07 target=_blank rel=noopener>ṚV. 3,38,7.</a> — 2. herbeischaffen, <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv10.056.html#rv10.056.02 target=_blank rel=noopener>ṚV. 10,56,2.</a> — Mit pra, pramita m. ˚ein Toter, <span class=ls>S I,150,2.</span> — Desid. sich über etwas (Akk.) eine richtige Vorstellung zu bilden wünschen, Bhāmatī 616,9. — Mit sam, sáṃmita, <span class=ls>Maitr. S. 2,11,1</span> (140,4).", "ru_html": "", "en_html": "mā¦ 15. mitá beside sáṃmita <span class=ls>Maitr. S. 2,11,1</span> (140,4). — With ā 1. to form, to bring forth, <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv03.038.html#rv03.038.07 target=_blank rel=noopener>ṚV. 3,38,7.</a> — 2. to procure, to bring (something), <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv10.056.html#rv10.056.02 target=_blank rel=noopener>ṚV. 10,56,2.</a> — With pra, pramita m. ˚a dead man, <span class=ls>S I,150,2.</span> — Desid. to wish to form a correct notion about something (Acc.), Bhāmatī 616,9. — With sam, sáṃmita, <span class=ls>Maitr. S. 2,11,1</span> (140,4).", "dcs": null, "src": ""}, {"tag": "4", "de_html": "Mā¦ ˚ = Lakṣmī, <span class=ls>S I,53,5</span> v.u. (Ko.); <span class=ls>Vās. 122,5.</span> — mā = Lakṣmī in mālava Prabandhacintāmaṇi 190,3; Kielhorn in EI 6,246, N. 12. — Sollte nicht māpatya bei Böhtlingk als mā + apatya zu fassen, d. h. mā hier = Lakṣmī sein? [Z.]", "ru_html": "Mā = Lakṣmī, <span class=ls>S I,53,5</span> v.u. (Ko.); <span class=ls>Vās. 122,5.</span> — mā = Lakṣmī в mālava Prabandhacintāmaṇi 190,3; Kielhorn in EI 6,246, N. 12. — Не следует ли māpatya у Бётлинка понимать как mā + apatya, то есть mā здесь = Lakṣmī? [Z.]", "en_html": "Mā¦ ˚ = Lakṣmī, <span class=ls>S I,53,5</span> q.v. (Ko.); <span class=ls>Vās. 122,5.</span> — mā = Lakṣmī in mālava Prabandhacintāmaṇi 190,3; Kielhorn in EI 6,246, N. 12. — Should not māpatya in Böhtlingk be understood as mā + apatya, i.e. should mā here be = Lakṣmī? [Z.]", "dcs": 4955, "src": "lexicographic"}, {"tag": "SCH-1", "de_html": "1. mā¦ mit Praes. damit nicht, <span class=ls>R. Gorr. 1,65,21.</span> purā mā mit Praes. so v.a. sonst, andernfalls,3,68,44. mā gantum arhasi metrisch statt na gan˚,2,116,5.", "ru_html": "1. mā с Praes. чтобы не; <span class=ls>R. Gorr. 1,65,21.</span> purā mā с Praes. = иначе, в противном случае, 3,68,44. mā gantum arhasi метрически вместо na gan˚, 2,116,5.", "en_html": "", "dcs": 4955, "src": "attested"}, {"tag": "SCH-15", "de_html": "3. mā¦ 15. mitá neben sáṃmita <span class=ls>Maitr. S. 2,11,1</span> (140,4).", "ru_html": "3. mā 15. mitá наряду с sáṃmita <span class=ls>Maitr. S. 2,11,1</span> (140,4).", "en_html": "", "dcs": 4955, "src": "attested"}, {"tag": "SCH-ā-1", "de_html": "— Mit ā 1. bilden, hervorbringen, <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv03.038.html#rv03.038.07 target=_blank rel=noopener>ṚV. 3,38,7.</a>", "ru_html": "— Mit ā 1. создавать, производить, <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv03.038.html#rv03.038.07 target=_blank rel=noopener>ṚV. 3,38,7.</a>", "en_html": "", "dcs": 4955, "src": "attested"}, {"tag": "SCH-ā-2", "de_html": "— 2. herbeischaffen, <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv10.056.html#rv10.056.02 target=_blank rel=noopener>ṚV. 10,56,2.</a>", "ru_html": "2. добывать, доставлять, <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv10.056.html#rv10.056.02 target=_blank rel=noopener>ṚV. 10,56,2.</a>", "en_html": "", "dcs": 4955, "src": "attested"}, {"tag": "SCH-pra", "de_html": "— Mit pra, pramita m. ˚ein Toter, <span class=ls>S I,150,2.</span>", "ru_html": "— Mit pra, pramita m. ˚умерший, <span class=ls>S I,150,2.</span>", "en_html": "", "dcs": 4955, "src": "attested"}, {"tag": "SCH-Desid.", "de_html": "— Desid. sich über etwas (Akk.) eine richtige Vorstellung zu bilden wünschen, Bhāmatī 616,9.", "ru_html": "— Desid. желать составить правильное представление о чём-либо (Akk.), Bhāmatī 616,9.", "en_html": "", "dcs": 4955, "src": "attested"}, {"tag": "SCH-sam", "de_html": "— Mit sam, sáṃmita, <span class=ls>Maitr. S. 2,11,1</span> (140,4).", "ru_html": "— Mit sam, sáṃmita, <span class=ls>Maitr. S. 2,11,1</span> (140,4).", "en_html": "", "dcs": 4955, "src": "attested"}]}, {"key": "m_a~~h0_zz_pwkvn", "h": "3. √mā (мерить) — PWKVN", "iast": "mā", "senses": [{"tag": "pwkvn-3-15", "de_html": "<b>3.</b> <i class=sa>mā</i>¦ 15〉 <i class=sa>mita</i> neben <i class=sa>saṃmita</i> <span class=ls>MAITR. S. 2,11,1 (140,4)</span>. — Mit <i class=sa>ā</i> 1〉 bilden, hervorbringen <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv03.038.html#rv03.038.07 target=_blank rel=noopener>ṚV. 3,38,7</a>. — 2〉 herbeischaffen <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv10.056.html#rv10.056.02 target=_blank rel=noopener>ṚV. 10,56,2</a>. — Mit <i class=sa>sam, saṃmita</i> <span class=ls>MAITR. S. 2,11,1 (140,4)</span>.", "ru_html": "", "en_html": "<b>3.</b> <i class=sa>mā</i>¦ 15〉 <i class=sa>mita</i> beside <i class=sa>saṃmita</i> <span class=ls>MAITR. S. 2,11,1 (140,4)</span>. — With <i class=sa>ā</i> 1〉 &#x27;to form, produce&#x27; <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv03.038.html#rv03.038.07 target=_blank rel=noopener>ṚV. 3,38,7</a>. — 2〉 &#x27;to procure, bring&#x27; <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv10.056.html#rv10.056.02 target=_blank rel=noopener>ṚV. 10,56,2</a>. — With <i class=sa>sam, saṃmita</i> <span class=ls>MAITR. S. 2,11,1 (140,4)</span>.", "dcs": null, "src": ""}, {"tag": "pwkvn-1", "de_html": "<b>1.</b> <i class=sa>mā</i>¦ mit <span class=ab>Präs.</span> damit nicht <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/ramayanagorr/?1,65,21 target=_blank rel=noopener>R. GORR. 1,65,21</a>. <i class=sa>purā mā</i> mit <span class=ab>Präs.</span> so <span class=ab>v. a.</span> sonst, andernfalls <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/ramayanagorr/?3,68,44 target=_blank rel=noopener>3,68,44</a>. <i class=sa>mā gantumarhasi</i> <span class=ab>st.</span> <i class=sa>na ga˚</i> metrisch <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/ramayanagorr/?2,116,5 target=_blank rel=noopener>2,116,5</a>.", "ru_html": "<i class=sa>mā</i> с <span class=ab>Präs.</span> чтобы не <a class=ls